name: Imaginarium #04
description:
Imaginarium Series

As we slip, carefully, warily, from one time to the next, it helps to remember there still exists beauty in this world. And time has its beauty too as it transports us from one space to the other; constantly shaping memory from past, to present, to future, it serves to remind us of the glamour of our Imaginarium.

A set of seven pieces to mark the transect of time - swapping one year for another – for the #HENJackpot ‘The Rocking New Year Jackpot’ event hosted by @rblbab @TerosEso @brainksy @ninacrypto2 and @Erythric

Artist: Steve Munro @SteveMunroArt || December 27th 2021 || PNG 7500 x 7500 || Hand-finished digital painting created by first advising machine learning before employing painterly techniques by hand in Adobe Creative Cloud.
